reviewText: It is a short take from the past. Good quality and Entertaining. Brings back old memories, as I enjoyed WC Fields as a young person. It will bring a smile.
Title: The Dentist

reviewText: A Classic updated to DVD. I bought this as a gift for my dentist and it was delivered quickly and sealed up tight.
summary: Still Funny After All These Years
Title: The Dentist

reviewText: I enjoy this short every time I see it; and I've seen it a hundred times. The scene with WC pulling the Lady's tooth was the raciest scene on film up until that time.
summary: Funny and typical W. C. Fields.
Title: The Dentist

reviewText: W.C. Fields is an original.  There will never be anything like him again.  The Dentist is a pre code sound short comedy film.  Fields is unleashed without any of the usual Hollywood varnish.
Title: The Dentist

reviewText: Video Quality was very poor, and I did not find this video funny at all. I was very disappointed in it.
Title: The Dentist

reviewText: I own a VHS copy of this short, but the streamed version is superior.  This film will be funny long after people forget what a dentist was.
Title: The Dentist
